data.title: Dalvin Cook - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Dalvin Cook: his birthday, what he did before fame, his family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Running back who was drafted by the Minnesota Vikings in the second round of the 2017 NFL Draft out of Florida State. He became one of the NFL's top running backs in 2019, starting the season with three straight 100-yard rushing efforts.

Before Fame

He was named a five-star recruit by Rivals.com after a standout career at Miami Central High School. He began his collegiate career at Florida State University in 2014.

Trivia

He finished his collegiate career at Florida State as the school's all-time leading rusher. He was named 2014 ACC Championship Game MVP after rushing for 177 yards and a touchdown and became the 2016 Orange Bowl MVP.

Family Life

He was born one of five siblings in Miami, Florida. His siblings names are Jamiya, Daneisha, Jameisha and Deandre.
